{"id":"810883371018452992","type":"text","timestamp":1773318644,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/810883371018452992","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://computationalcalculator.tumblr.com/post/810529031624736768/the-date-isnt-included-in-the-screenshot-but-a\">computationalcalculator</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/citrusmillie/721264152648237056\">citrusmillie</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/batzzzzz/721260785919295488\">batzzzzz</a>:</p><blockquote><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"602\" data-orig-width=\"800\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s640x960/58d6186bd01a10bae25198b76fa6ed35640450f1.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"602\" data-orig-width=\"800\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s75x75_c1/f0086f8ce6577288988736316cecc5ac76dea4a6.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s100x200/f7bbdd97cd7af24520d4518295eea4b23aa1f3c9.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s250x400/1916e3a43524de6eb95f9739be8f7fa7cbcfb4ef.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s400x600/72842b3f49de7662ab11ca5f17bb3b49a038e47f.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s500x750/5deb102caa542048f06bdc22029db7b378ccbd87.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s540x810/5a805fedeae1743e9699c3c2fdd9f6120617caaf.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s640x960/58d6186bd01a10bae25198b76fa6ed35640450f1.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/261981e45359466f079e76dc40df5f14/71042e5bdf9ac7b6-75/s1280x1920/625781ec04cf2c4b34896941101b895221be1e63.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/></figure></div><p>Rool</p></blockquote><p>all tumbrlinas come from a common ancestor</p></blockquote><p>The date isn’t included in the screenshot, but a quick reminder that Usenet (site this is from) dates everything post-1993 as “1993-09-[number of days since sept 1993]”, as a nod to Eternal September</p></blockquote>\n<p><b>I do miss some of the unique things from the old Usenet days:</b></p><p class=\"npf_chat\">*Ascii Art - Requires that &ldquo;fixed bitch font,&rdquo; lol<br/>*In Line Replies<br/>*Wackylacing (Which requires in line replies to work properly)<br/><br/>And for those that don&rsquo;t know about &ldquo;Eternal September.&rdquo;  Every September, when the new college semester would begin, all these new folks would gain Internet access and thus access to Usenet and every September would be flooded with new users who had not yet learned the Netiquette of the era.  Only, things didn&rsquo;t go back to normal after September 1993, when  a bunch of ISPs added Usenet access and especially AOL in early 94.<br/><br/>God, I&rsquo;m an old lady, lol.<br/><br/><br/>Alexandria<br/>…<i>who often ended her posts like this, as was the style at the time.</i></p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"batzzzzz","active":true,"theme":{"header_full_width":640,"header_full_height":640,"header_focus_width":640,"header_focus_height":359,"avatar_shape":"circle","background_color":"#CA0707","body_font":"Helvetica Neue","header_bounds":"0,640,359,0","header_image":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/be56e075fb662b1c314e535f1ad4a134/c9db728581c21452-af/s640x640/f82ae7f1753990617bfc7001303825213c63199a.jpg","header_image_focused":"https://64.media.tumblr.com/be56e075fb662b1c314e535f1ad4a134/c9db728581c21452-af/s2048x3072_c0,0,100000,56094/4addd6f10d6217104fae9e39de889f6ed06ed70b.jpg","header_image_poster":"","header_image_scaled":"https://